      <title>油價穩定，因美國經濟擔憂而每週下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-steadies-heads-weekly-drop-us-economy-worries-2024-05-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由於歐佩克+繼續減產的前景，週五早盤油價小幅上漲，但由於美國經濟不確定性以及以色列與哈馬斯戰爭造成的有限原油供應中斷，原油基準指數將每週下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-steadies-heads-weekly-drop-us-economy-worries-2024-05-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 00:52:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
